Home / Our  Businesses / Product Identification  
ASTRONOVA PRODUCT IDENTIFICATION


AstroNova Completes Acquisition of European Digital Printing Manufacturer TrojanLabel
Press Release

AstroNova™ Product Identification provides labeling solutions for a competitive edge from tabletop label printers to industrial label presses and specialty printers to minimize label warehousing expenses and provide greater flexibility in packaging operations to improve our customers’ ability to identify, track, and market their products.

With decades of experience QuickLabel® provides the best solution for tabletop label printing systems. Our label printers, software, label media and ink are designed to work in harmony. From vibrant product labels to GHS certified labels, we understand your needs. With our easy to use color label printing systems, you save time, gain flexibility and increase sales. Other products include barcode printers, and labeling software that allow businesses to print their own labels on-demand and just in time. QuickLabel has continued to develop innovative labeling solutions specifically for manufacturers and processors who want to print product labels in-house. These printing solutions are ideal for processors and manufacturers in the food , cosmetics and personal care, chemical processing, dietary supplement, pharmaceutical, and medical device industries.
QuickLabel branded products include:

Kiaro! inkjet color label printers
QL product line of color label printers
Pronto! barcode printers
Label and ink supplies
Software and accessories

With its broad range of entry-level, mid-range, and high-performance tabletop label printers, QuickLabel provides customers with a continuous path to upgrade to new products.

Since 2012, TrojanLabel™ has globally revolutionized color printing technology with the production of digital color label presses and specialty printing systems for a broad range of end markets. Products include an advanced digital label printing press, and overprinting system that allow label converters and manufacturers to print labels or print high quality, 4-color print directly onto flat ink absorbing surfaces including cardboard, paper bags, flat wooden planks. Along with the stand alone color label presses, they offer a digital color print station OEM modules for label converters, print shops, brand owners, contract packaging and the secondary labels/logistics markets, secondary labels/logistics market manufacturers as well as many others. TrojanLabel has become the obvious choice for anyone considering an industrial or specialty printing systems and continues to develop innovative solutions specifically for industrial printing applications.
TrojanLabel branded products include:

TrojanOne label printer for private branding
TrojanTwo industrial mini press designed for label converters
TrojanThree industrial grade overprinting system

TrojanLabel products are known for their innovative design and superior performance.





 
Visit QuickLabel Visit TrojanLabel 






