Home / Our  Culture / Core Values  
Core Values
AstroNova operates its business on a platform of core values. These guide our company’s processes and practices as we build a growing, profitable business.
Customers first: superior customer satisfaction is our ultimate goal

We build lasting and trusting relationships with our customers.
We create value for our customers by providing world-class products and services.

One global team: great people make great companies

We are committed to attract, protect, develop and retain the best talent.
We operate with high integrity and mutual respect.
We manage by facts and are driven by data.
We tackle challenges with purpose and efficiency.

Innovation: leading edge innovation accelerates our growth

We are committed to developing new and creative ways to add customer value.

Continuous improvement: driven by the AstroNova Operating System (AOS) is our way of life

We are focused on continuously improving our products, services, and processes.

Building shareholder value: strong profits and cash flow build shareholder value and mutual prosperity

We act like owners and are rewarded for value creation.












