Home / Our  Culture  
Our Culture
AstroNova has ingrained a strong and definable company culture that shapes the way it operates and engages with stakeholders. It consists of four key components:

A powerful set of core values guides our employees’ behavior and dictates the way business is conducted.
The AstroNova Operating System (AOS) helps us manage the business to achieve continuous improvements in quality, delivery, cost, and growth.
A commitment to operating with integrity and compliance ensures business is conducted in an honest, legal, and environmentally responsible manner.
A passionate commitment to quality drives our goal to achieve zero defects and understand the changing needs and expectations of our customers.












