AstroNova’s TrojanLabel™ Unit Forms International Distribution Alliance with Nilpeter A/S
AstroNova, Inc. (NASDAQ: ALOT), a global leader in data visualization technologies, today announced that its TrojanLabel ApS business unit and Nilpeter A/S have established an international distribution agreement for the Trojan2 mini digital label press. Under the agreement, the Trojan2 will be marketed and distributed through Nilpeter’s subsidiaries in the United States , Brazil , the Asia-Pacific , the United Kingdom and Ireland . This Smart News Release features multimedia. View the full release here: http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20170719005602/en/ AstroNova’s TrojanLabel ApS business unit and Nilpeter A/S have established an international distribution agreement for the Trojan2 mini digital label press. The Trojan2 will be marketed and distributed through Nilpeter’s subsidiaries in the United States , Brazil , the Asia-Pacific , the United Kingdom and Ireland . (Photo: Business Wire) “Our strategy is to offer a wide range of digital solutions with our PANORAMA product...





06-29-17
AstroNova Receives Multiple Commitments for ToughWriter 640 Narrow Format Flight Deck Printer
AstroNova, Inc. (NASDAQ: ALOT), a leading manufacturer and supplier of aerospace products, including printers, networking hardware and related accessories to commercial, business and military customers, today announced that it has received multiple commitments following the Paris Air Show from major airlines for the ToughWriter 640 narrow format flight deck printer to be installed in their Boeing 737 aircraft. “We are excited by the strong customer response to the ToughWriter 640 as we see the accelerated adoption of this next-generation flight deck printer by airlines throughout the world,” said AstroNova President and CEO Greg Woods. The ToughWriter 640 brings several performance and operational benefits to the B737 aircraft. Compared with competitive offerings, the ToughWriter 640 provides a weight reduction of nearly 50%, a significant improvement in reliability, lower power consumption and a compact form factor. The ToughWriter 640 offers a number of industry firsts, including...



